QuestData.Title: Moving In
QuestData.Description: Hiya! The name's Tore. I head up the mining operation here at K3... or I will shortly anyway!$B$BThis here cave is full of creepy-crawlies. I think we could do with a few less spiders before we move in - what'd you think?
QuestData.LogDescription: Tore Rumblewrench outside of Crystalweb Cavern wants you to kill 12 Crystalweb Spiders.
QuestData.CompletionText: Be careful near that dispenser! Those things are dangerous.
QuestData.RewardText: Ha ha! Good to see you're up for some dirty work.$B$BMuch appreciated there, pal!
